{"tid":1465423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線唔係大撚哂！","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:38:27.000Z","uid":84104,"like":36,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1db02e5b042f68c137912c017ba6c8e7568e80bb","tid":1465423,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"冇大台唔等於冇共識<br />\n<br />\n叫你走 班狗嚟緊又屌人散水撚<br />\n話有鬼又屌人分化撚<br />\n叫你地冷靜又話要尊重前線，話人割席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問下今日機場邊個係屬於前線呀！！<br />\n前線大撚哂呀？<br />\n肯尊重其他人未呀！<br />\n成班失哂控！<br />\n有事就話有鬼煽動 咁明知有鬼你仲受人煽動？<br />\n<br />\n大家都反省下自己<br />\n諗下場運動係由好多人組成<br />\n繼續比仇恨完全覆蓋自己就會搞彎成個運動<br />\n我地已經唔可以輸<br />\n要贏就要互相聽大家意見！<br />\n而唔係少數嘅前線騎劫所有人嘅意見<br />\n然後第二日比人屌又屌返人割你席"},{"pid":"11e8eaeac4c8d6fddf8471e6b7411bf8d41e8a65","tid":1465423,"uid":48584,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"where are you"},{"pid":"40d92b26e12b464649d88587dd8710ca1b527cf5","tid":1465423,"uid":4346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"入機場屌前線囉"},{"pid":"964110c8b75b40f2179eed1ab7ca9bbd16f415f9","tid":1465423,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40d92b26e12b464649d88587dd8710ca1b527cf5","tid":1465423,"uid":4346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"入機場屌前線囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"哦 你落場踢囉"},{"pid":"9bce8c554eee5daa9d5d642557a501cbfc634318","tid":1465423,"uid":259812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"有得預防就預防，發生咗就不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n所以我想講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心有鬼煽動啊！！勿情緒主導！</span>"},{"pid":"c3bed69e27689b79d1ef47e7cb95b20b5a079611","tid":1465423,"uid":84104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11e8eaeac4c8d6fddf8471e6b7411bf8d41e8a65","tid":1465423,"uid":48584,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"where are you"},"citedBy":